items.title: Dozens killed in Goa nightclub fire
items.standfirst: At least 25 people have been killed after a fire at a Goa nightclub, police in the Indian state have said.
items.content: At least 25 people have been killed after a fire at a Goa nightclub, police in the Indian state have said.
